room_title: Escape room "The Study" by The Ville Escape Room in Kirksville
review: The Study is an excellent room! The owners Stephanie and Aaron have done an amazing job with both of the rooms and I can't wait to try more rooms in the future! So fun and challenging!

room_title: Escape room "The Study" by The Ville Escape Room in Kirksville
review: Had an amazing experience in The Study! It was hard, but my friends and I loved the challenge! Can't wait for the next room!
